{
  "id": "6a1585ab57ba301b98d9e67c",
  "title": "後発人狼系の構造的回避策",
  "created": 1779795373,
  "updated": 1779799502,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a1585ab57ba301b98d9e67c",
      "text": "後発人狼系の構造的回避策",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795373,
      "updated": 1779795373
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585a3000000000017de84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795373,
      "updated": 1779795373
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585ab000000000017dead",
      "text": "[tokoroten.icon]のClaudeのログから自動抽出された記事",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795381,
      "updated": 1779795381
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585ab000000000017deae",
      "text": "---",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795381,
      "updated": 1779795401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb1",
      "text": "[人狼ゲームの構造的衰退] の弱点を、後発成功作はどう設計で潰したか。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb2",
      "text": "[客観情報が乏しい集団の必然帰結] の対症療法集。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb4",
      "text": "[*** Among Us]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb5",
      "text": "\t[* タスク] = 死人にもやることを与える (脱落者の暇問題解消)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb6",
      "text": "\t[* ボディ発見] = 客観情報を継続的に生成する仕組み",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb7",
      "text": "\t→ 「客観情報の供給が乏しい」前提を崩した",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deb9",
      "text": "[*** ワンナイト人狼]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deba",
      "text": "\t試合を [* 5〜10分に圧縮]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017debb",
      "text": "\t「脱落者の暇時間」自体を消す",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017debc",
      "text": "\t→ 短さで構造問題の影響を最小化",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017debd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017debe",
      "text": "[*** ワードウルフ]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017debf",
      "text": "\tCOも役職体系もなくす",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec0",
      "text": "\t[* お題のズレ] = 観察可能な情報だけで成立",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec1",
      "text": "\t→ メタゲーム化の余地そのものを排除",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec3",
      "text": "[*** Avalon (レジスタンス)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec4",
      "text": "\tクエスト結果が [* 公開される客観情報] として継続生成",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec5",
      "text": "\t誰も脱落しない (30-45分通しでプレイ)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec6",
      "text": "\tMerlin/Percival/Assassin で情報非対称の妙味",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec7",
      "text": "\tただし高度なメタ戦略・社会的テンプレに依存する側面は残る",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dec9",
      "text": "[*** 共通の処方箋]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017deca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017decb",
      "text": "table:table29",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017decc",
      "text": " 弱点\t処方",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017decd",
      "text": " 客観情報の乏しさ\tタスク/ボディ/クエスト結果で継続的に生成",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017dece",
      "text": " 脱落者の暇\t死人にタスク付与 or 試合を短縮 or 脱落自体を排除",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017decf",
      "text": " メタ言語肥大\tCO/役職体系を廃止、観察事実だけで成立させる",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017ded0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017ded1",
      "text": "[*** 含意]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017ded2",
      "text": "新ゲーム設計時は、 [客観情報が乏しい集団の必然帰結] の3条件のうち[* 少なくとも1つを潰す]ことで",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795391
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1585b4000000000017ded3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779795391,
      "updated": 1779795393
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1594af0000000000bb670d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779799215,
      "updated": 1779799215
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1594af0000000000bb670e",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779799215,
      "updated": 1779799217
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1594b00000000000bb6710",
      "text": "\t[フィード ザ クラーケン]あたりも[人狼]の構造的弱点への回答例として印象的だった",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779799217,
      "updated": 1779799348
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1595ab0000000000bb6711",
      "text": "\t[犯人は踊る]は[ワンナイト人狼]の系譜かもなあ。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779799467,
      "updated": 1779799481
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1595b90000000000bb6712",
      "text": "\t[ワードウルフ]系のアプローチは、先行して[お邪魔者]や[エセ芸術家ニューヨークへ行く]があった気がする",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779799481,
      "updated": 1779799502
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1594b00000000000bb670f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779799217,
      "updated": 1779799217
    }
  ]
}